{"article_id":"6J6zbTuwSMjWzoPx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"When the Supreme Court in 2015 recognized a constitutional right","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"for same-sex couples","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to marry ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"it was a huge step forward for equality ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"but the ruling didn ' t resolve the deep religious divisions over gay marriage","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that endure .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"One of those battles arrives Tuesday at the Supreme Court , a case","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"in which Colorado baker Jack Phillips cites his religious and free expression rights","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"for refusing in 2012 to design a custom cake for a gay couple ' s wedding .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"It is a landmark battle","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that , in essence , pits the baker ' s right","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"to practice his Christian faith","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"against the rights of Charlie Craig and David Mullins","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"to be free from discrimination","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"as they go about their public lives .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Respecting religious rights is one of the nation 's fundamental values ,","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"but so is respecting the rights of individuals","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"to be treated equally .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"OPPOSING VIEW :","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"Here 's why I can ' t custom-design cakes for same-sex weddings","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"In front of the justices , the arguments will be couched in the complexities of the First Amendment ' s guarantee of free expression :","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Phillips argues","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that his artistic cakes express his ideas about marriage","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and are entitled to full constitutional protection .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"But the battle also comes down to a simple idea","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"enshrined in American law and values :","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"When you open a business in this country","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and sell to the public ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"you agree to abide by public accommodation laws .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"On those grounds , the Colorado Civil Rights Commission and a state appeals court ruled against Phillips .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"unless the Supreme Court decides to turn its back on that core principle of equality ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"it should do the same .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"For the court to rule otherwise","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"would open the door to discrimination by all sorts of vendors","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"who claim artistic expression :","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"photographers , chefs , suit and dress designers , florists and wedding planners ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"to name a few .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"While the First Amendment ' s guarantee of freedom of religion and expression are both fundamental rights ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"neither is unlimited .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"An old saying ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" Your right","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"to swing your arms","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"ends just where the other man ' s nose begins , \"","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"is apropos .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Phillips has an absolute right to his religious beliefs ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"but","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"when the practice of his religion infringes on the rights of others to equal treatment ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"it goes too far .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"In the past , the Supreme Court has set limits on freedom of speech and religion .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"The court has repeatedly ruled","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that constitutional rights do not nullify neutral laws on everything from racial equality to taxes .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"An Amish farmer , for example , refused to pay Social Security taxes for workers","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"based on his religious belief","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that the community and not the government should care for the elderly and needy .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"The Supreme Court ruled unanimously in 1982","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"by becoming an employer ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"the farmer freely entered into commercial activity","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"and accepted certain limits on the exercise of his beliefs .","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"Forty-five states have public accommodation laws","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that prohibit discrimination on the grounds of race , gender , ancestry and religion .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Twenty-two also prohibit discrimination on the basis of sexual orientation .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Colorado is one of them .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Phillips and his lawyers try to make a distinction :","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"The baker isn ' t discriminating against gay people","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"because he ' s willing to sell them anything off his store shelves ,","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"but he is not willing to use his artistry","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"to celebrate their marriage .","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"No doubt","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"he is sincere .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"Even so , the distinction does not change the fact","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"that Mullins and Craig and others will be summarily turned away ,","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"if the court rules for Phillips .","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"Of course they can get a cake somewhere else ,","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"which Mullins and Craig did .","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"That 's not the point .","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"They were humiliated","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"and treated as second-class citizens","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"when Phillips turned them away .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"In passing the Civil Rights Act of 1964 ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"the Senate recognized","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that discrimination `` is about the humiliation , frustration and embarrassment","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"that a person must surely feel","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"when he is told that he is unacceptable as a member of the public","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"because of his race or color. \"","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"Or , today ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"because he loves someone of the same sex","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"and chooses to get married .","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"Allowing that sort of unequal treatment is not what America is about .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"The public will be better served","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"if the Supreme Court puts a stop to it now .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"If you ca n't see this reader poll ,","depth":2},{"id":93,"text":"please refresh your page .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":111,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":108,"right":110,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":99,"right":107,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":96,"right":3,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":0,"right":95,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":101,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":6,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare